DocAttribute.Name: RelatingBuildingElement
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to ~~building~~ element in which a void is created by associated ~~opening~~ feature subtraction element. > IFC2x PLATFORM CHANGE: The data type has been changed from IfcBuildingElement to IfcElement with upward compatibility for file based exchange.

DocAttribute.Name: RelatedOpeningElement
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the ~~opening~~ feature subtraction element which defines a void in the associated ~~opening~~ element. > IFC2x PLATFORM CHANGE  The data type has been changed from IfcOpeningElement to IfcFeatureElementSubtraction with upward compatibility for file based exchange.
